<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.6">
<l>ceṉṟu vārcilai vaḷaitti laṅkaiyai</l>
<l>veṉṟa villiyār vīra mēkolō</l>
<l>muṉṟil peṇṇaimēl muḷarik kūṭṭakat</l>
<l>taṉṟi liṉkura laṭaru meṉṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What [about] the heroism of the archer who,</l>
<l>Going to Laṅkā, bending the long bow, conquered [it]?</l>
<l>The call of the black ibis in its twiggy nest</l>
<l>Atop of the courtyard palm assaults me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
